{"tid":2255964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不受拜登醜聞影響，700經濟學家經濟學諾貝爾獎得主發公開信反特朗普連任","createTime":"2020-10-24T03:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T08:42:27.000Z","uid":333488,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6193ab0833746779304ee41cb264c53030b3a41a","tid":2255964,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"近700位經濟學家，包括七位諾貝爾經濟學獎得主，發表公開信強烈反對美國總統川普連任，並列舉一連串罪狀，包括「持續踐踏」民主、抗疫不力和散播「危險的不實資訊」。<br />\n<br />\n簽署這封公開信的經濟學家包括任職主要機構的重量級學者，包括剛摘下<br />\n2020年諾貝爾經濟學獎桂冠的米格羅姆（Paul Milgrom）、2016年得主哈特（Oliver Hart）、2012年得主羅斯（Alvin Roth），以及2001年得主阿克洛夫（Akeorge Akerlof）。阿克洛夫是前聯準會（Fed）主席葉倫的丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n這些經濟學家在公開信上說：「基於這些理由，我們強烈建議選民做別人無法代你們做的事：用選票把川普趕下台，藉此重申民主權。」川普陣營尚未立即對此發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/econagainsttrump/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Feconagainsttrump%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=a6e3d73d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/econagainsttrump/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇題睇題donald Trump 真係仇家遍天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c2ce3518bd389c4c191296ecb6362f117be526","tid":2255964,"uid":3465,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBuAGP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBuAGP7.jpg&h=51bf9b66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d294e4ce6c591fe32da24ee6b87db92fbf097ba","tid":2255964,"uid":70013,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"小市民：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/ff4581/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_200930/20200930_a2edeb62260309ed22a6Fp1a7fbNcY77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fff4581%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2